name: "Errar"- Aida Rojas (feat. Hilandera)
description: The last year in this date I released this song called "Errar" which is a song asking for forgiveness to one of my lovers. This song was recorded in the living room of my old apartment in Barquisimeto, Lara (Venezuela) and it has the collab of Hilandera (@vocesferales) in the harmonies and mixing.
